<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='418370' id='t-418370'>And all of this without causing</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='419919' id='t-419919'>a massive explosion
of energy consumption --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='422395' id='t-422395'>because of the solar cells,
